name: VoidLoop.Rotate(shift)
description:
Seeking catharsis, insight, and healing
We phase through versions of our selves
Exploring the relationship between them
Past selves emphasizing lessons learned
Present selves looking back and forward
Future selves encouraging our successes
Introspective topographies of evolution

In the evening, the loop will display in inverted colors. During the day, it will be in its regular dark void self state.
This modified variant utilizes Voltaine's DAY NIGHT open source code, which can be found here:
https://github.com/voltaine1/daynight
https://hen.link/Voltaine 

See suspension.nyc for more about the original suspension project, "Phasing."
